Login/ security logs( Run power shell as admin)
Get-WinEvent -LogName Security | Where -Object {$_.Id - in 4624, 4625, 4634} (4624- successfully login, 4625- failed login, 4634- log off)
Get-EventLog -LogName Security -Newest 10 (“last 10 security logs”)                  -To Check last 10 days login activities
”
