Get-NetIpConfiguration(“ network adapter “)               -To get network adapter details
Get-NetTCPConnection (@ active TCP Connections”)          -shows all TCP connection of system to network
Get-NetAdapter (“network Interfaces”)                      -shows all network interfaces (Wi-Fi, Ethernet, etc.).
Get-DnsClientServerAddress (“DNS servers”)                  -shows the DNS servers your system is using.
Test-Connection url (“ping test”)                           -To check ping 
